params.name: preprocessor
params.description: (PreTrainedTokenizerBase, FeatureExtractionMixin, or ImageProcessingMixin):The preprocessor associated with this model configuration.

params.name: batch_size
params.description: The batch size to export the model for (-1 means dynamic axis).

params.name: num_choices
params.description: The number of candidate answers provided for multiple choice task (-1 means dynamic axis).

params.name: seq_length
params.description: The sequence length to export the model for (-1 means dynamic axis).

params.name: is_pair
params.description: Indicate if the input is a pair (sentence 1, sentence 2)

params.name: framework
params.description: The framework (PyTorch or TensorFlow) that the tokenizer will generate tensors for.

params.name: num_channels
params.description: The number of channels of the generated images.

params.name: image_width
params.description: The width of the generated images.

params.name: image_height
params.description: The height of the generated images.

params.name: sampling_rate
params.description: The sampling rate for audio data generation.

params.name: time_duration
params.description: Total seconds of sampling for audio data generation.

params.name: frequency
params.description: The desired natural frequency of generated audio.
